show list of tags in my playbook
---------------------------------
$ ansible-playbook --list-tags site.yaml

run palaybook
---------------
$ ansible-playbook --ask-become-pass site.yaml

run task for specific tags
----------------------------
$ ansible-playbook --tags "centos,db" --ask-become-pass site.yaml
# this run tasks that have "tages: centos" and "tags: db" and "tags: always".


